The paper proposes a novel framework for deep neural networks and focuses on image classification tasks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the optimization of the ensemble members, which suggests a possible fit with cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper uses natural language processing techniques to describe the proposed method, which could also make it relevant to cs.CL (Computation and Language).
